<br>
In a limited sense, what if activating the LFG tag allowed others to see your level and class?  In a roleplay sense, maybe you've left word at the local taverns, and the grapevine is circulating the information that Swiftwind the ranger of 40 seasons is looking for a brave group of companions to adventure with.  This way you have the option of &quot;roleplaying&quot; yourself as a low key, relatively anonymous figure of the shadows or as a mercenary type who is willing to group with whomever, as long as the adventure is fierce and the bounty worth your while.<br>
<br>
